413 affects condominium and noncondominium community ownership association
424 developments, review efforts in other states to address problems with community
435 ownership associations and consider adoption of the Uniform Common Interest Ownership
446 Act. The stakeholder group is required to submit a report to the Joint Standing Committee
457 on Housing and Economic Development, which may submit legislation related to the report
468 to the Second Regular Session of the 132nd Legislature.
